{"id":1338,"date":"2017-12-07T08:43:12","date_gmt":"2017-12-07T08:43:12","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/?page_id=1338"},"modified":"2017-12-18T12:36:25","modified_gmt":"2017-12-18T12:36:25","slug":"testimonial-2","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/testimonial-2\/","title":{"rendered":"Testimonial 2"},"content":{"rendered":"<section class=\"wpb-content-wrapper\"><p>[vc_row full_width=&#8221;stretch_row&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1509622163169{padding-top: 50px !important;padding-bottom: 90px !important;background-image: url(https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/background.jpg?id=1154) !important;}&#8221;][vc_column]<div class=\"rt-vc-testimonial-2\">\n\t<h3 class=\"rtin-section-title\" style=\"\">Our Happy Students<\/h3>\n\t<div class=\"owl-theme owl-carousel rt-owl-carousel\" data-carousel-options=\"{&quot;nav&quot;:false,&quot;dots&quot;:true,&quot;autoplay&quot;:true,&quot;autoplayTimeout&quot;:&quot;5000&quot;,&quot;autoplaySpeed&quot;:&quot;200&quot;,&quot;autoplayHoverPause&quot;:true,&quot;loop&quot;:true,&quot;margin&quot;:30,&quot;responsive&quot;:[{&quot;items&quot;:1}]}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rtin-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"rtin-item-content\" style=\"\">I thoroughly enjoyed courses from here and hope to expand on my gained knowledge about making apps. The courses as well as the examples are well presented, easy to follow and engaging.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rtin-item-title\" style=\"\">Tony Walker<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rtin-item-designation\" style=\"\">Apps Developer<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rtin-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"rtin-item-content\" style=\"\">The courses here exceeded my expectations in many regards, especially in the depth of information supplied. In a very non-threatening environment, I learned key principles of design that I can implement immediately.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rtin-item-title\" style=\"\">Martin Brian<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rtin-item-designation\" style=\"\">UI Designer<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rtin-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"rtin-item-content\" style=\"\">Excellent content and assignments that build on your knowledge, reinforce, and then expand. I recently secured new employment using PHP and couldn&#039;t have done so without the Professional Web Development courses.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rtin-item-title\" style=\"\">David Fahim<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rtin-item-designation\" style=\"\">Web Developer<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n<\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n<\/section>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row full_width=&#8221;stretch_row&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1509622163169{padding-top: 50px !important;padding-bottom: 90px !important;background-image: url(https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/background.jpg?id=1154) !important;}&#8221;][vc_column][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-1338","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/1338","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/wp-j